<p>Thanks a bunch for the people who made this possible from a PR standpoint (on top of the amazing product): Mitchell, John, Schrep, Beltzner, Paul, Mary, Melissa, Nicole, the Outcast team, Anne-Julie, Jane, Giuliano, Francesco, Pascal, Abdulkadir, Victoria, Dominique, Sian, Ben, Ralf, Thomas, Pierre, H?l?ne, Antoine, Juan, Belen, Nukeador, Guillermo, Diana, Giuseppe, Zbigniew, Agnieszka, Magda, Piotr, Jolanta, Stas and every community members<sup>[<a href="#pnote-3555-2" id="rev-pnote-3555-2">2</a>]</sup> that have been involved in the PR part of this amazing launch...</p>


